<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَيَأْتِيهِ رِزْقٌ سَابِغٌ مِنْهُ سَائِغٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَرُوحُ لَهُ طَوْلاً وَيَغْدُو لَهُ فَضْلا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمَا هُوَ يَسْتَدْعِي غِذَاءً بِقِيمَةٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلا هُوَ مِمَّنْ يُحْسِنُ الشُّرْبَ وَالأَكْلا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>جَرَى فِي مَجَارِي عِرْقِهِ بِتَلَطُّفٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>بِلا طَلَبٍ جَرْيًا عَلَى قَدْرِهِ سَهْلا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَأَجْرَى لَهُ فِي الثَّدْيِ لُطْفَ غِذَائِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>شَرَابًا هَنِيئًا مَا أَلَذَّ وَمَا أَحْلا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَأَلْهَمَهُ مَصًّا بِحِكْمَةِ فَاطِرِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَالشُّكْرُ الْجَزِيلُ بِمَا أَوْلا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَأَخَّرَ خَلْقَ السِّنَّ عَنْهُ لِوَقْتِهَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَأَبْرَزَهَا عَوْنًا وَجَاءَ بِهَا طَوْلا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَقَسَّمَهَا لِلْقَطْعِ وَالْكَسْرِ قِسْمَةً<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلِلطَّحْنِ أَعْطَى كُلَّ قِسْمِ لَهَا شَكْلا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَصَرَّفَ فِي لَوْكِ الطَّعَامِ لِسَانَهُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>يُصَرِّفُهُ عُلْوًا إِذَا شَاءَ أَوْ سُفلا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلَوْ رَامَ حَصْرًا فِي تَيَسُّرِ لُقْمَةٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَأَلْطَافِهِ فِيمَا تَكَنَّفَهَا كَلا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَكَمْ خَادِمٍ فِيهَا وَكَمْ صَانِع لَهَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>كَذَلِكَ مَشْرُوبٌ وَمَلْبَسُهُ كلا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَكَمْ لُطْفٍ مِنْ حَيْثُ تَحْذَرُ أَكرَمَتْ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَمَا كُنْتَ تَدْرِي الْفَرْعَ مِنْهَا وَلا الأَصْلا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>